headline: LII Q2 Deep Dive: Margin Gains, Refrigerant Transition, and Product Portfolio Expansion
summary: Climate control solutions innovator Lennox International (NYSE:LII) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 3.4% year on year to $1.50 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $7.82 per share was 13.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
